snippet.title: Darkwater World Exclusive Reveal Trailer – PC Gaming Show: Most Wanted 2024
snippet.description:
Darkwater is a 1-4 player cooperative horror shooter where players must stock, manage and pilot their own submarine as they explore a mysterious ocean. Springing a leak will be the least of your worries in Darkwater’s deadly abyss.
